text:
The Denver Broncos have clearly had a QB problem post Peyton Manning after he retired and many people have said that Bo Nix is the best post Manning Broncos QB. There has been fourteen different Dennver starting QBs since then. Only seven of those fourteen have started eight games or more and have even started a WR at QB.
The most important position has been an unstable shit show over the past ten years with the Broncos and fans have been fed up with it. Fans think that Bo Nix is the savior of Denver football so lets take a look at how he and all the others between stack up to one of the greatest football players of all time.


